=== 操作方式 ===
阴毛可以以多种方式去除，如上蜡、[[剃毛|剃刀]]、[[糖化|糖化]]、雷射除毛或{{le|化学脱毛膏|Chemical depilatory}}。以歐美女性常用的熱蠟脫毛為例，將熱蠟融化後，將熱蠟敷在想要去除的陰毛上並。在蠟開始慢慢硬化時以小布條覆蓋在蠟上。當蠟充分硬化時，快速撕去布條。蠟隨著小布條被撕去時，黏在蠟上的毛髮也被從根部拉出。臘除毛可以在家中私下使用工具或在沙龍、水療中心請美容師協助進行<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.cosmopolitan.com/style-beauty/beauty/advice/a2857/bikini-line-hair-removal/|title=Get a Perfect Bikini Line|date=2009-03-10|newspaper=Cosmopolitan|accessdate=2018-10-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319185741/https://www.cosmopolitan.com/style-beauty/beauty/advice/a2857/bikini-line-hair-removal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

脫毛蜡一般使用天然[[蜂蜡|蜂蜡]]和{{le|妥尔油|tall oil}}的混合而成，與腿部脱毛常用的合成蜡不同<ref>Susan Cressy & Margaret Rennie, ''Beauty Therapy Fact File'', page 293, Heinemann, 2004, ISBN 0-435-45142-1</ref>。蜂蜡被認為在去除粗糙阴毛时更为有效。此外，阴毛抑制剂可以减缓、甚至完全阻止陰毛再生，持续效果可长达两个月<ref>Ian Denchasy, ''Art of Oral Sex: Bring Your Partner to New Heights of Pleasure'', page 30, Quiver, 2007, ISBN 1-59233-290-0</ref>。

=== 脫毛後護理措施 ===
撕除脫毛蠟的過程可能会产生疼痛或不適，但在一般的情况下可能持續數秒至數分鐘不等，通常不會持續超过五天<ref>Hilda Hutcherson, ''Pleasure'', page 190, Perigee, 2006, ISBN 0-399-53286-2</ref>。有些人會在脫毛前後進行一些減輕疼痛的措施，在打蠟前一小時左右服用溫和的消炎藥物（如[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]）可能有助於減少脫毛過程中的潛在疼痛<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/39633447|title=Johns Hopkins family health book|last=Klag|first=Michael J.|last2=|first2=|date=1999|publisher=HarperCollins|year=|isbn=0062701495|edition=1st ed|location=New York|pages=|chapter=|oclc=39633447}}</ref>。局部麻醉劑也可用於減輕疼痛<ref name=":0" />。[[怀孕|怀孕]]女性的陰部會更為敏感，因此懷孕期間進行脫毛的不適感可能會更加強烈<ref>Linda Murray, Leah Hennen & Jim Scott, ''The Babycenter Essential Guide to Pregnancy and Birth'', page 576, Rodale, 2005, ISBN 1-59486-211-7</ref>。

脫毛後可能還會有一些殘留的毛髮，可以使用鑷子或電剪去除殘餘的孤立毛髮<ref name="Ovat">{{cite book|title=SalonOvations' Advanced Skin Care Handbook|url=https://archive.org/details/salonovationsadv0000scho|author2=Shari Miller Sims|author3=Shari Sims|date=1994|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=1-56253-045-3|pages=[https://archive.org/details/salonovationsadv0000scho/page/94 94]-95|author1=Lia Schorr}}</ref>。在脫毛後的幾天將蛋油（Egg oil）敷在脫毛部位表面能夠減少發炎、疼痛以及細菌生長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23467945|title=Anti-inflammatory and analgesic effects of egg yolk: a comparison between organic and machine made|accessdate=2015-09-05|date=2013-02-17|publisher=National Library of Medicine|website=PubMed.gov|archive-date=2018-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827210001/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23467945|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随着長时间脫毛習慣的建立，阴毛會逐漸變得脆弱，生长也會逐渐緩慢，脫毛的頻率可能會下降，以至於不用頻繁的脫毛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.womansday.com/Articles/Beauty/Waxing-101-Tips-and-Tricks-for-Beginners.html|title=Bikini and Brazilian Waxing Tips - Hair Removal Facts at WomansDay.com|accessdate=2010-11-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707091332/http://www.womansday.com/Articles/Beauty/Waxing-101-Tips-and-Tricks-for-Beginners.html|archivedate=2010-07-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

