ks?id=CLHeHGFlQiYC&pg=PA325#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate=2013-05-09|year=2002|publisher=Anova Books|isbn=9781844110025|page=25|quote=Salons offer a choice of waxing styles for women, including the widely renowned Brazilian or Mohican for those concerned not to reveal a single stray pube in the inciest, winciest beachwear, while The Hollywood denotes the full monty.|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727104749/https://books.google.com/books?id=CLHeHGFlQiYC&pg=PA325#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。'''Naturall'''、'''au naturel'''或灌木丛式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.salon.com/mwt/feature/2008/12/11/bush_back/ |title=Bush is back |last1=Germinsky |first1=Lisa |date=2008-12-11 |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2013-05-09 |archive-date=2009-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501044811/http://www.salon.com/mwt/feature/2008/12/11/bush_back/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不带有任何修建或造型，而是修剪或剪短的阴毛，没有移走或修型，大腿内侧的则剃光。有些女性要求修建，但在保留阴唇的毛发的同时脱掉阴阜的阴毛。

