'''巴西式脱毛'''指去除[[盆骨|盆骨]]区正面和背面的所有毛发，但有时会在[[阴阜|阴阜]]留下一条薄的发带<ref name=milady/>{{Rp|139}}<ref name=essort/><ref name=BrBi/><ref name=SalE/><ref name=Boston>{{cite book | author = Boston Women's Health Book Collective, The | year = 2005 | title = Our Bodies, Ourselves: A New Edition for a New Era | url = https://archive.org/details/ourbodiesoursel00bost | publisher = Touchstone/Simon & Schuster | location = New York | page = [https://archive.org/details/ourbodiesoursel00bost/page/4 4] | isbn = 0-7432-5611-5 |edition=35th anniversary}}</ref>。巴西式可用于穿着丁字裤比基尼的人士<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jeffries |first1=Fran |url=http://blogs.ajc.com/better-health/2009/03/19/a-ban-on-brazilian-bikini-waxing/ |title=A ban on ‘Brazilian’ bikini waxing? |publisher=Better Health (blog) |work=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution |date=2009-03-19 |accessdate=2013-05-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023074402/http://blogs.ajc.com/better-health/2009/03/19/a-ban-on-brazilian-bikini-waxing/ |archivedate=2012-10-23 }}</ref>，是比基尼脱毛款式之一。它完全除去从臀部及邻近区域到[[肛门|肛门]]、[[会阴|会阴]]及[[外阴|外阴]]（大阴唇和阴阜）的毛发<ref name=salon>{{cite web|url=http://dir.salon.com/story/health/feature/1999/09/03/bikini/ |title=Faster Pussycat, Wax! Wax!, |date=1999-09-03 |author=Valhouli, Christina |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2007-05-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070515094254/http://dir.salon.com/story/health/feature/1999/09/03/bikini/ |archivedate=2007-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name=BVio>{{cite book | author = Blue, Violet | year = 2002 | title = The Ultimate Guide to Cunnilingus | publisher = Cleis Press | location = San Francisco | page = 66 | isbn = 1-57344-144-9}}</ref>。巴西式脱毛也被称为完全巴西式脱毛、完全比基尼脱毛、好莱坞式脱毛或斯芬克斯式（以[[斯芬克斯猫|斯芬克斯猫]]的名字命名）<ref name=milady/>{{Rp|139}}<ref name=BrBi/><ref name=SalE/>。巴西式脱毛在现代首次被1987年在曼哈顿开办的J.Sisters美容院命名，这家美容院由来自巴西的Padilha七姐妹创办<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2011/12/the-new-full-frontal-has-pubic-hair-in-america-gone-extinct/249798/|title=The New Full-Frontal: Has Pubic Hair in America Gone Extinct?|author=Ashley Fetters|date=2011-12-13|accessdate=2011-12-15|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203171418/https://www.theatlantic.com/health/archive/2011/12/the-new-full-frontal-has-pubic-hair-in-america-gone-extinct/249798/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

巴西式脱毛比其他款式更具争议性<ref name=KirM>
{{cite book| author = Kirsch, Melissa| year = 2006| title = The Girl's Guide to Absolutely Everything| url = https://archive.org/details/girlsguidetoabso00meli| publisher = Workman Publishing| location = New York| page = [https://archive.org/details/girlsguidetoabso00meli/page/424 424]| isbn = 0-7611-3579-0}}</ref><ref name="Joannides (2006)">{{cite book| author = Joannides, Paul| year = 2006| title = Guide to Getting It On| publisher = Goofy Foot Press| location = Waldport, Oregon, USA| isbn = 1-885535-69-4}}</ref>{{Rp|528}}。跟所有脱毛款式一样，脱毛前后身体会经历痛苦<ref name=salon/><ref name="Joannides (2006)"/>{{Rp|531}}<ref>{{cite book| author = Blue, Violet| year = 2002| title = The Ultimate Guide to Cunnilingus| publisher = Cleis Press | location = San Francisco, California USA | page = 67| isbn = 1-57344-144-9}}</ref><ref name=GodS>{{cite book| author = Godson, Suzi| year = 2005| title = Sexploration: An Edgy Encyclopedia of Everything Sexual| url = https://archive.org/details/sexplorationedgy0000gods| publisher = Amorata Press| location = Berkeley, California USA| isbn = 1-56975-505-1}}</ref>{{Rp|161}}，其中有些人认为如果被异性的合作伙伴舔阴，就更为不舒服了<ref name="Joannides (2006)"/>{{Rp|page233}}<ref name=GodS/>{{Rp|89}}。美国女演员、模特儿{{le|丽莎·巴布希亚|Lisa Barbuscia}}对她第一次在洛杉矶的流行美容院与色情明星做巴西式的痛苦经历：“这真是太痛苦了，我都晕倒了，几乎要被送往医院，我发誓再也不试第二次了<ref>{{cite web|title=Guide to Brazilian wax job|url=http://www.thehairfacts.com/waxing-brazilian.htm|website=Hairfacts.com|accessdate=2015-09-05|archive-date=2020-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106033500/http://www.thehairfacts.com/waxing-brazilian.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”然而，反对这种经验评价的声音很普遍。该过程的一些批评人士认为，巴西式脱毛能使成年女子看上去像女孩，声称这可能是它在[[性行业|性行业]]知名的原因<ref name=Boston/><ref name=KirM/><ref name=GodS/>{{Rp|161}}。美容专家的克里斯蒂娜·瓦尔霍利（{{lang|en|Christina Valhouli}}）认为这种脱毛不自然<ref name=Boston/><ref name="Joannides (2006)"/>{{Rp|246}}<ref>{{cite book| author = Feldman, David| year = 1987| title = Why Do Clocks Run Clockwise?| url = https://archive.org/details/whydoclocksruncl00feld| publisher = HarperCollins| location = New York| page = [https://archive.org/details/whydoclocksruncl00feld/page/146 146]| isbn = 0-06-074092-2}}</ref>，如果不正当操作还会带来健康风险，而且免疫系统差的人士做了之后有感染的风险<ref name=Tweed>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,288860,00.html |title=Woman Almost Dies After Bikini Wax |author=Katherine Tweed |accessdate=2007-07-31 |work=Fox News |date=2007-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713175134/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C288860%2C00.html |archivedate=2007-07-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，進行巴西式脱毛後的女性大陰唇閉合得比較完整，加上女性陰毛有向下引流尿液的作用。因此，女性小便時尿液會沿著陰唇流到大腿內側{{Citation needed}}。

== 健康 ==
必备的贴片测试通常在大腿的最上部分进行，用来测试客户是否对蜡过敏，皮肤是否反应过度。由于外阴[[黏膜|黏膜]]是比基尼区域中最敏感的，通常放在最后进行。有时会导致毛发向内生长的肿块。

医学界近来发现脱毛或剃光比基尼区域阴毛的女性患上[[毛囊炎|毛囊炎]]或毛囊周围受感染的几率有所增加<ref>{{cite book|author1=Barbara Hackley|author2=Jan M. Kriebs|author3=Mary Ellen Rousseau|title=Primary Care of Women: A Guide for Midwives and Women's Health Providers|date=2006|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|isbn=0-7637-1650-2|pages=833}}</ref>。其中一些感染可发展成更严重的囊肿，需要用手术刀切口、为脓肿排水和抗生素。[[金黄色葡萄球菌|金黄色葡萄球菌]]是毛囊炎的最常见致病菌<ref>{{cite news|title=Bikini line waxing and shaving poses infection risk|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/health-21832543|accessdate=2015-09-05|agency=BBC News|date=2013-03-19|archive-date=2018-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180105092646/http://www.bbc.com/news/health-21832543|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

家庭医生艾蜜丽·吉布森博士（{{lang|en|Emily Gibson}}）表示剃阴毛“（相当于）去除了防止摩擦的保护垫，会留下微小的开放性伤口，令你遭受感染”<ref>{{cite news|author1=Emily Gibson|title=Pubic hair has a job to do – stop shaving and leave it alone|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/aug/07/pubic-hair-has-job-stop-shaving?INTCMP=SRCH|accessdate=2015-09-05|agency=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2012-08-07|archive-date=2012-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120810222049/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/aug/07/pubic-hair-has-job-stop-shaving?INTCMP=SRCH|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

全球[[阴虱|阴虱]]病例的显著减少要归功于比基尼脱毛<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazilian Bikini Waxes Make Crab Lice Endangered Species|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-13/brazilian-bikini-waxes-make-crab-lice-endangered-species-health.html|work=Bloomberg|accessdate=2013-10-26|author=Jason Gale|author2=Shannon Pettypiece|date=2013-01-13|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310235908/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-13/brazilian-bikini-waxes-make-crab-lice-endangered-species-health.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=女性剃除阴毛的利弊分析|url=http://health.youth.cn/fk/201410/t20141015_5838637.htm|website=中国青年报|accessdate=2015-09-04|date=2014-10-15}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

2009年3月，美国[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]计划施行禁止比基尼脱毛的法案，但在遭到美容院老板的强烈反对后被取消<ref>{{cite web|title=US bikini wax ban plans ditched|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7956689.stm|website=BBC News|accessdate=2015-09-05|date=2009-03-21|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414111846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7956689.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

